==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lumpenproletariat
<hw>Lump`en*pro*le*tar"i*at</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Politics)</fld> <def>the lowest level of the proletariat,
comprising unskilled workers, the unemployed, and the dispossessed,
alienated from the class with with they would normally identify and
having little or no class solidarity; -- an important element in Marxist
theory.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lumper</ent>⟦br⟧
